### Test 03: Add a new rankings successfully
### Positive test 
### We assume that the token has been aquired by the login request.
# @name newrankings
POST {{BASE}}/rankings 
Content-Type: application/json 
Token: {{token}} 

{
	"person_id": ###REPLACE###,
	"date": ###REPLACE###,
	"position": ###REPLACE###
} 

### Check the created rankings

@newrankingsid = {{newrankings.response.body.lastId}}
GET {{BASE}}/rankings/{{newrankingsid}}
Content-Type: application/json 

